{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-433-steps-in-euclids-algorithm","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-401-to-480","demoType":null,"title":"Izazov 433: Korak u Euklidovom algoritmu","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Neka $E(x_0, y_0)$ bude broj koraka potrebnih za određivanje najvećeg zajedničkog delioca brojeva $x_0$ i $y_0$ pomoću Euklidovog algoritma. Preciznije:</p>\n<p>$$\\begin{align}\n&#x26; x_1 = y_0, y_1 = x_0\\bmod y_0 \\\\\n&#x26; x_n = y_{n - 1}, y_n = x_{n - 1}\\bmod y_{n - 1}\n\\end{align}$$</p>\n<p>$E(x_0, y_0)$ je najmanje $n$ za koje važi $y_n = 0$.</p>\n<p>Imamo nas $E(1, 1) = 1$, $E(10, 6) = 3$ i $E(6, 10) = 4$.</p>\n<p>Definišite $S(N)$ kao zbir $E(x, y)$ za $1 ≤ x$, $y ≤ N$.</p>\n<p>Tuna $S(1) = 1$, $S(10) = 221$ na $S(100) = 39\\,826$.</p>\n<p>Pronađi $S(5 \\times {10}^6)$.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f51d1000cf542c51002f","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302104,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-433-steps-in-euclids-algorithm"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function stepsInEuclidsAlgorithm() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nstepsInEuclidsAlgorithm();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>stepsInEuclidsAlgorithm()</code> inapaswa kurudisha <code>326624372659664</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(stepsInEuclidsAlgorithm(), 326624372659664);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-401-to-480","dashedName":"problem-433-ste